         <note type="other" othertype="DITA insight">This
close match of simpletable to tabular, regular data makes simpletable suitable
as the basis for specialized structures such as <xref href="properties.xml">properties</xref> (for programming information) and <xref href="choicetable.xml">choice tables</xref> (for tasks).</note>
